name: Endless abyss of data
description:
Info from developer: This project was created for mini game jam and will be developed in future. First build may have some bugs which will be fixed in nearest days.

All sounds are from freesound.com, photos from unsplash.com and logos from freepic.com. More detailed attribution will be added soon. 

In a world where people's lives are governed by the Internet, is there a place in this endless abyss of data from where data is deleted and brings death to a person?
